headline: Health Trends Can’t Stop This Stock and Its 7% Dividend Yield
summary: Altria  stock has plenty of problems.  The share of adults that smoke has declined to less than 12% today from 15% in 2015, according to the American Lung Association.  While Wall Street analysts see 2026 sales as flat or slightly down, per-share earnings should benefit from buybacks.
